                <h1>Gandhigiri'24</h1>
                <p>Welcome to Gandhigiri 2024, an exciting annual event hosted by CS Department of <b>Axis Institute of Technology and Management</b>, where innovation and creativity merge with the timeless values of simplicity and sustainability, inspired by the teachings of Mahatma Gandhi. This year's event, themed “Technology for a Better Tomorrow,” is a unique platform where students, tech enthusiasts, and innovators can showcase their cutting-edge projects across both hardware and software domains. The event reflects Gandhi’s vision of a world where progress and technological advancements coexist harmoniously with nature and human welfare. Through Gandhigiri 2024, we aim to encourage the next generation of thinkers and creators to use technology not just for profit or convenience, but to solve the critical issues our society faces, from sustainability and resource efficiency to equitable access to modern solutions.</p>
                <br>
                <p>Gandhigiri 2024 is designed to be a dynamic showcase of technology, featuring several projects that span a wide array of disciplines, including hardware prototypes, software applications, and hybrid solutions that combine the best of both worlds. Students and participants have been working tirelessly on these projects to demonstrate how technology, when applied thoughtfully, can simplify life and make the world a better place. Whether it's creating innovative IoT-based devices that can enhance daily life, or developing powerful software that can transform industries, Gandhigiri 2024 serves as a breeding ground for ideas that push boundaries while staying rooted in the core principles of simplicity, sustainability, and inclusiveness. This event isn’t just about technology – it's about using technology to reflect and fulfill the ideals of self-reliance, non-violence, and constructive problem-solving, all of which were central to Gandhi’s philosophy.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <h2>What is Gandhigiri 2024?</h2>
                <p>Gandhigiri 2024 is a unique and inspiring event designed to bring together students, tech enthusiasts, and budding innovators from diverse fields to showcase groundbreaking projects that blend hardware and software technologies. This one-of-a-kind gathering not only celebrates innovation but also embodies the spirit of problem-solving through simplicity, echoing the ideals of Mahatma Gandhi. Drawing inspiration from Gandhi's timeless principles of self-reliance, non-violence, and sustainable development, the event aims to foster creative solutions that address real-world challenges. Participants are encouraged to explore how technology can be used to build a more equitable, eco-friendly, and peaceful future.</p>
